Author: Komodo-Bot#0171
Content:
[Instel7#1416] Komodo platform announced:
This is a massive upgrade in technology for the entire Komodo ecosystem. Please note that this update is a hard fork. It is, therefore, a mandatory update.
- Sapling Upgrade
- VerusHash algorithm, bringing near-equality between CPUs and GPUs with the fastest CPU mining algorithm in the world
- VerusPoS algorithm, allowing for a 50/50 hybrid blockchain, which can be combined with either 50% VerusHash or 50% Equihash for the proof of work component.
- Time Locking, which allows mined rewards to be time-locked for random release, within a set of parameters.
- The ‚ÄúEras‚Äù parameter (ac_eras), allowing 3 eras of different coin emission schedules to be defined which alter emission, including slow start options, and linear exponential decay at specific, predetermined block height schedules.

Author: Komodo-Bot#0171
Content: [PTYX#6840] We had a meeting with the Chameleon devs last week and the team was working on the home screen, send, and receive functions. Most of the frontend work is don't. They are now working on "connecting" it all with Agama core. I have another meet on Monday to ibstall the app and analyze the beta.

Author: Komodo-Bot#0171
Content: [PTYX#6840] We are working based on sprints and they have been keeping a good pace but what backtracked us was the original design work. It took longer than expected. I'm pushing to have a public beta out before the end of the year. If for some reason I think that won't happen we'll make an announcement and adjust the delivery times on the roadmap.

Author: Komodo-Bot#0171
Content: [PTYX#6840] We are also working on a video update that should be published on the 1st about the ico. We have reduced the amount of tokens we will sell. There will only be 2.5 million zilla in circulation for the year and it's likely we won't need to do a second round of funding at all. The goal was moved down from 2.25M to 350K. Just enough to finish our token generation apps and polish the other tools that are already available.
